* Sunrise / sun set should trigger the start of this.
http://api.usno.navy.mil/rstt/oneday?date=today&loc=Sugar%20Hill,%20GA

* It should also calcualte the length of the overnight period required.

* Capture command:
echo Capture night stars
sudo raspistill -w 1920 -h 1080 -t 43200000 -tl 10000 -o /var/www/html/frame%05d
.jpg
* This will do 12 hours (43200000)
